\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Focus.
\f0\b0  Drains while you pay attention. If it hits zero you're fully checked out: the transcript literally blurs into "something something Q3 something synergy," and if you get called on in that state, you're cooked.\
\ls1\ilvl0
\f1\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Visibility.
\f0\b0  The Goldilocks meter, and the second big idea. Too low and the boss notices you've said nothing: "You've been quiet, thoughts?" Too high and you're clearly engaged, which means you're clearly available: action items gravitate toward you. You want to hover in the invisible middle. Camera-off regenerates Focus but tanks Visibility toward the danger zone.\
\ls1\ilvl0
\f1\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Action Items.
\f0\b0  Three and you lose. They stick to you through dodges, deflections, and one horrifying event where you get assigned one while on mute.\
