\f1\b \cf0 The action item hot potato
\f0\b0 \
Periodically the boss says "we need someone to own this." A standoff triggers: you and 2-3 coworkers, everyone silent, tension bar filling. Your options: hold still (someone else might crack), fake a cough, "I think Greg's really close to this one." Deflecting works but builds that coworker's Resentment, and resentful coworkers deflect back at you later with better odds. Volunteer takes the item but grants a big Visibility cushion. If nobody cracks before the bar fills, the boss assigns it to whoever has the highest Visibility. The whole social physics of meetings in one minigame.\

